title: Who won Celebrity Big Brother 2017? Coleen Nolan crowned winner in grand final
text:
AND THE WINNER IS... Who won Celebrity Big Brother 2017? Coleen Nolan crowned winner in grand final 
The series has beeen full of rows, laughs and tears - with Coleen finally emerging as victor by helen thomas Comments AFTER months of waiting and speculation Celebrity Big Brother is now over. 
The final is now over and fans voted in their droves to crown Coleen Nolan as the victor with Jedward as runners up . Channel 5 8 Celebrity Big Brother presenters Emma Willis and Rylan Clark-Neal 
So who were the contestants in the final and what were their odds of winning? Find out if the bookies got it right… Kim Woodburn – 3rd 8 Kim has recently been back in the spotlight, appearing on ‘Celebrity 100% Hotter’ 
A surprise addition to the house on Friday 13 January was How Clean is Your House star Kim Woodburn, who entered the house alongside Chloe and Jessica .
